</pre><p><strong>5</strong>. Open <strong>dimens.xml</strong> located under <strong>res â values</strong> and add the below values.</p><pre class="brush: xml; title: dimens.xml; notranslate" title="dimens.xml">
&lt;resources&gt;
    &lt;!-- Default screen margins, per the Android Design guidelines. --&gt;
    &lt;dimen name=&quot;activity_horizontal_margin&quot;&gt;16dp&lt;/dimen&gt;
